data.description: Gorgeous custom home w/ completely separate 845 SF accessory dwelling unit all nestled on 4.75 private acres. Main house has 1,300 SF wraparound covered porch/patio with w/pine soffits & exposed beams. Beautiful & cozy living rm w/a big gas fireplace, built-ins & window seat reading nook. Large open kitchen w/gas range, farm sink, floating shelves & lots of cabinets. Walk-thru pantry & laundry both have sinks & cabinet space. Primary bedroom on main w/dbl. vanity, freestanding soaker tub, walk-in steam shower & walk-in closet.  Upstairs there's a nice rec rm & 2 large bedrooms both w/ensuite baths. Private ADU sits 100' away w/1 bed, 1.25 baths, W/I shower  & closet. Kitchen open to living w/vaulted ceilings. Office/den & one car garage.
